@startuml
title Сценарий 5: Переполнение цифрового реестра
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

participant "Auditor" as Auditor
participant "AuditProtocol" as Protocol
participant "DigitalRegistry" as Registry
participant "FinancialReport" as Report

Auditor -> Protocol : Sign("SIG-999")
activate Protocol
Protocol --> Auditor : Valid
deactivate Protocol

Auditor -> Registry : AddEntry(protocol.Id)
activate Registry
note right of Registry : Registry.IsFull == true
Registry --[#blue]> Auditor : return false (Rejected)
deactivate Registry

Auditor -> Report : SetStatus(Rejected)
activate Report
Report --> Auditor
deactivate Report

note over Registry : Ошибка записи: достигнут лимит хранилища
@enduml